---
title: "Diagramma 5 - Modello Dati Progetti"
---

classDiagram
    %% Focus su gestione progetti
    
    class MarkunoApiTools {
        <<Tool>>
        +GetProjects(onlyMy) Task~string~
        +ProjectExists(identifier, matchById) Task~string~
        +CreateProject(receiverId, des, note) Task~string~
        +OpenProject(projectName, receiverId) Task~string~
    }
    
    class Project {
        <<Model>>
        +Id: int
        +Des: string
        +Status: string
        +DtCrea: double
        +DtMod: double
        +Importo: double
        +User: User
        +Note: string
        +Cognome: string
        +Nome: string
        +Email: string
    }
    
    class ProjectsResponse {
        <<DTO>>
        +Level: int
        +Time: int
        +Data: ProjectsData
        +Path: string
    }
    
    class ProjectsData {
        <<DTO>>
        +HasMore: bool
        +Data: List~Project~
        +Fields: List~ProjectField~
    }
    
    class ProjectField {
        <<DTO>>
        +Cod: string
        +Des: string
        +Type: string
        +Visible: bool
        +Sort: bool
    }
    
    class User {
        <<Model>>
        +Id: int
        +Name: string
        +Level: int
    }
    
    class MarkunoAPI {
        <<External>>
        POST /muconf/plist
    }
    
    ProjectsResponse *-- ProjectsData : contiene
    ProjectsData *-- Project : contiene 0..*
    ProjectsData *-- ProjectField : contiene 0..*
    Project --> User : owner 0..1
    
    MarkunoApiTools --> MarkunoAPI : richiesta progetti
    MarkunoAPI ..> ProjectsResponse : risponde
    MarkunoApiTools ..> Project : gestisce
    
    note for MarkunoApiTools "Operazioni Progetti:\n- GetProjects: lista progetti\n- ProjectExists: verifica esistenza\n- CreateProject: crea via SignalR\n- OpenProject: apre via SignalR"
    
    note for Project "Informazioni progetto:\n- Dati anagrafici cliente\n- Timestamp creazione/modifica\n- Stato e importo\n- Owner (utente)"
